high_descs: Walk forward to the wall, make a right, then walk over and face the kitchen island that is on your right.
Pick up the egg that is on the kitchen island, in front of the tomato.
Turn to the left, walk past the oven, then turn left to face the dishwasher.
Heat up the egg in the microwave before taking it back out.
Turn left, walk a few steps, then turn left again to face the kitchen island.
Place the egg on the kitchen island, above the oven.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated egg on the kitchen island.

high_descs: Move forward and turn right at the island and face it on the right.
Pick up the egg from the right side, but closer to the loaf of bread.
Hold the egg and turn to the left and face the microwave on the left.
Open the microwave and place the egg inside. Then open the microwave and take the egg out, and shut the door.
Hold the egg and turn to the left and then face the island on the left.
Place the egg in the front portion of the island, centered and in front of the tea pot.
anns.task_desc: Heat an egg and move it to the counter.
Heat an egg and return it to the table
